WEBVTT

00:05.048 --> 00:07.398
-[THEME MUSIC]

00:12.882 --> 00:16.886
-♪ SOME PEOPLE STAND
IN THE DARKNESS ♪

00:17.017 --> 00:20.585
♪ AFRAID TO STEP
INTO THE LIGHT ♪

00:20.716 --> 00:24.589
♪ SOME PEOPLE NEED
TO HELP SOMEBODY ♪

00:24.720 --> 00:27.984
♪ WHEN THE EDGE OF
SURRENDER'S IN SIGHT ♪

00:28.115 --> 00:30.726
♪ DON'T YOU WORRY

00:30.856 --> 00:33.816
♪ IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT

00:36.949 --> 00:38.821
♪ 'CAUSE I'M ALWAYS READY

