28:42.851 --> 28:45.941
♪ LIKE THE LIGHT BREAKING

28:46.072 --> 28:49.336
♪ THROUGH THE SHADOWS

28:49.466 --> 28:52.731
♪ YOU'RE ALL I SEE

28:52.861 --> 28:57.736
